page_title: What's new in Azure OpenAI Service?
page_description: Learn about the latest news and features updates for Azure OpenAI.
chunk_content: July 2023### Support for function calling- Azure OpenAI now supports function calling to enable you to work with functions in the chat completions API.### Embedding input array increase- Azure OpenAI now supports arrays with up to 16 inputs per API request with text-embedding-ada-002 Version 2.### New Regions- Azure OpenAI is now also available in the Canada East, East US 2, Japan East, and North Central US regions. Check the models page, for the latest information on model availability in each region.
